10:09.376 --> 10:12.744
No man can lift
a tiny lady like that.

10:12.746 --> 10:14.446
You're finally watching
that movie, huh?

10:14.448 --> 10:17.716
I know I promised
I'd take Bevy out dancing,

10:17.718 --> 10:19.684
but I can't do it.

10:19.686 --> 10:20.785
I'll look stupid.

10:20.787 --> 10:22.821
Since when do you care
about how you look?

10:22.823 --> 10:25.757
You spend half your life
puttering around this house

10:25.759 --> 10:26.524
in your underpants.

10:26.526 --> 10:27.859
Well,
that's about comfort.

10:27.861 --> 10:30.195
It's also a warning shot
to outsiders

10:30.197 --> 10:31.062
that you're not welcome.

10:31.064 --> 10:32.497
All I'm saying is,
you always

10:32.499 --> 10:35.033
care less about what other
people think.

10:35.035 --> 10:35.800
Why is this different?

10:35.802 --> 10:37.535
Let me be honest
with you.

10:37.537 --> 10:38.770
[ Sighs ]

10:38.772 --> 10:40.972
I don't like
to move my body.

10:40.974 --> 10:41.740
Yeah, we've met.

10:41.742 --> 10:43.408
Now, the thing is,
I'm afraid.

10:43.410 --> 10:47.512
Dancing in front of
all those people with
their judgy eyes --

10:47.514 --> 10:48.279
I-i can't do it.

10:48.281 --> 10:52.017
Well, you'll never know how
you'll look if you don't try.

10:52.019 --> 10:55.220
<i> Pops was right.</i>
<i> My dad had to see for himself.</i>

10:55.222 --> 10:59.391
<i> Luckily, he spotted</i>
<i> my trusty camera.</i>

10:59.393 --> 11:00.291
<i> And, with no one around,</i>

11:00.293 --> 11:03.228
<i> he decided to give dancing</i>
<i> a shot.</i>

11:03.230 --> 11:06.097
<i> He grooved, he grinded,</i>

11:06.099 --> 11:06.965
<i> he gyrated,</i>

11:06.967 --> 11:09.067
<i> he did...whatever</i>  this  <i> is.</i>

11:09.069 --> 11:12.237
Look at me!
Ha ha ha!

11:12.239 --> 11:13.638
I'm a guy who dances now!

11:13.640 --> 11:16.608
<i> He danced like no one</i>
<i> was watching,</i>

11:16.610 --> 11:17.642
<i> and luckily, no one was.</i>

11:17.644 --> 11:20.278
Just a reminder,
I will be performing

11:20.280 --> 11:24.015
with with my barbershop
quartet, the princi-pals,

11:24.017 --> 11:25.750
at the open mike thursday...

11:25.752 --> 11:27.185
¶ Ni-i-ght ¶

11:27.187 --> 11:29.220
Stop the announcements.
We need to talk.

11:29.222 --> 11:30.055
No, no, no, no, no!

11:30.057 --> 11:31.890
We had an agreement
over stern eye contact

11:31.892 --> 11:34.426
that if I gave in to your
daughter's dance demands,

11:34.428 --> 11:36.227
you would stay far away
from my office.

11:36.229 --> 11:39.597
But that was before I realized
that you were right

11:39.599 --> 11:40.632
and there can be no dance.

11:40.634 --> 11:42.467
But you forced me
to flip-flop!

11:42.469 --> 11:43.735
I flipped!
I can't flop back!

11:43.737 --> 11:47.105
I didn't know how dirty
that dance was gonna be!

11:47.107 --> 11:49.808
Which is why I wanted it
to be a soda pop hop!

11:49.810 --> 11:52.110
It was my favorite dance
as a teen,

11:52.112 --> 11:53.244
but no one's embraced it.

11:53.246 --> 11:54.946
<i> Well,</i>
<i> I'm embracing it, Earl.</i>

11:54.948 --> 11:57.415
<i> Fine! The dirty dance</i>
<i> is once again dead.</i>

11:57.417 --> 12:00.351
<i> One thing -- my daughter,</i>
<i> Erica, must never know</i>

12:00.353 --> 12:02.153
<i> that I had anything</i>
<i> to do with this.</i>

12:02.155 --> 12:04.289
[ Whispering ]
I think that's your mom!

12:04.291 --> 12:06.458
Yes, thank you, Lainey!

12:06.460 --> 12:08.159
¶

12:08.161 --> 12:09.494
You.

12:09.496 --> 12:10.428
Hey!

12:10.430 --> 12:13.865
What's up, best friend
who's also my daughter?

12:13.867 --> 12:15.867
The PA. System was on
the whole time.

12:15.869 --> 12:20.038
The whole school heard
every crazy word you said.

12:21.141 --> 12:21.606
Oopsie.

12:21.608 --> 12:23.475
You completely
betrayed me.

12:23.477 --> 12:24.743
Who does that?!

12:24.745 --> 12:26.344
A normal mama
who loves you

12:26.346 --> 12:27.011
and you love back?

12:27.013 --> 12:28.613
For once, I thought
we were a team

12:28.615 --> 12:30.582
and had something
in common.

12:30.584 --> 12:32.016
Turns out,
we never will.

12:32.018 --> 12:34.285
<i> As Erica left my mom</i>
<i> feeling low,</i>

12:34.287 --> 12:37.455
<i> my dad was still high</i>
<i> on his sweet moves.</i>

12:37.457 --> 12:39.924
Hoo-hoo!
Look at me go!

12:39.926 --> 12:43.495
I have to admit, at first,
I was a little bit nervous,

12:43.497 --> 12:46.264
but now [Laughing]
Look at me!

12:46.266 --> 12:47.932
[ Click, music stops ]

12:50.437 --> 12:51.736
Burn this.

12:51.738 --> 12:52.470
I'm sorry?

12:52.472 --> 12:55.140
This must never be seen
by anyone.

12:55.142 --> 12:55.974
I'm not following.

12:55.976 --> 12:57.175
If you love my daughter,

12:57.177 --> 12:59.344
you won't do any
of this ever again.

12:59.346 --> 13:02.881
You said I wouldn't know if
I could dance until I tried.

13:02.883 --> 13:04.616
Well, you tried
and now we know.

13:04.618 --> 13:07.352
You cannot
and should not dance.

13:07.354 --> 13:09.554
¶
Look at this.

13:09.556 --> 13:10.488
Oh, no!

13:10.490 --> 13:12.223
Adam, no, turn away!

13:12.225 --> 13:13.291
It'll change you forever!

13:13.293 --> 13:16.761
Oh, no, no, no!
What am I looking at?!

13:16.763 --> 13:17.595
Turn away!

13:17.597 --> 13:19.430
I want to, but I can't.

13:19.432 --> 13:21.132
It's like the ark
from "raiders"!

13:21.134 --> 13:23.001
You promised
you wouldn't judge me,

13:23.003 --> 13:25.336
but I'm feeling a lot
of judging right now.

13:25.338 --> 13:28.339
Don't make yourself
the victim in this.

13:28.341 --> 13:29.941
That boy is the victim.

13:29.943 --> 13:32.477
All I did was walk
into the room.

13:32.979 --> 13:35.480
Okay, I know
you're super pissed at mom.

13:35.482 --> 13:37.148
Well, I got good news.

13:37.150 --> 13:39.350
Let my sanctuary
heal you!

13:39.352 --> 13:43.221
I come here to release
my angry rage
that I always have.

13:43.223 --> 13:43.755
How?

13:43.757 --> 13:44.622
A little thing called...

13:44.624 --> 13:46.891
The angry dance.
That's not a thing.

13:46.893 --> 13:50.094
Tell that to Kevin Bacon's
body double in "Footloose."

13:50.096 --> 13:51.462
[ <i>  "footloose" plays</i>  ]

13:51.464 --> 13:53.298
Go on. Angry-dance!

13:53.300 --> 13:56.067
Unleash your pain with tumbles
and flips!

13:56.069 --> 13:56.734
You're an idiot.

13:56.736 --> 13:57.802
I'm trying
to help you here.

13:57.804 --> 14:00.071
The only thing you're doing is
proving what a dope you are.

14:00.073 --> 14:01.773
Your words
make me so angry!

14:01.775 --> 14:04.576
Dance it out, Barry.
Dance it out.

