¶

15:44.878 --> 15:46.945
<i> Yep, Erica was a girl</i>
<i> on a mission --</i>

15:46.947 --> 15:51.082
<i> make a squeaky-clean dance</i>
<i> a little more dirty.</i>

15:51.084 --> 15:52.216
Baby has the watermelon.

15:52.218 --> 15:53.017
-Roger.
