15:58.358 --> 16:02.360
Hey, dude, some guy,
like, barfed on your van.

16:02.362 --> 16:03.628
What? Who?

16:03.630 --> 16:06.564
Who? Uh...me?

16:06.566 --> 16:08.232
I'll kill you!

16:08.234 --> 16:10.368
<i> It was a needlessly</i>
<i> intricate plan</i>

16:10.370 --> 16:12.603
<i> that was ready</i>
<i> to rock 'n' roll --</i>

16:12.605 --> 16:15.073
<i> that is,</i>
<i> until Barry rolled up.</i>

16:15.075 --> 16:16.040
It's boom time!

16:16.042 --> 16:18.443
Stop! I don't know
what this is, but stop!

16:18.445 --> 16:19.210
It's a confetti cannon.

16:19.212 --> 16:22.146
Now cut-up paper will
endlessly rain down on us

16:22.148 --> 16:24.382
like in the final scene
of "footloose."

16:24.384 --> 16:24.882
I told you --

16:24.884 --> 16:27.251
this is "dirty dancing,"
Not "footloose"!

16:27.253 --> 16:28.686
Hello?
An authority figure

16:28.688 --> 16:30.421
has banned us
from moving our bodies.

16:30.423 --> 16:33.358
Seriously, Erica,
I pity you.

16:33.360 --> 16:34.525
I pity you both.

16:34.527 --> 16:36.127
There is no way
I'm letting you

16:36.129 --> 16:38.763
ruin this wonderful
soda pop hop!

16:38.765 --> 16:39.364
Both of you, out!

16:39.366 --> 16:41.632
If I'm going out,
I'm going out dirty!

16:41.634 --> 16:42.934
Hit it, Lainey!

16:42.936 --> 16:44.302
<i> And just like that,</i>

16:44.304 --> 16:45.370
<i> my sister took</i>
<i> a leap of faith.</i>

16:45.372 --> 16:48.272
¶  <i> Now I've Had</i>
