¶

17:11.431 --> 17:12.196
Tell me where she is,

17:12.198 --> 17:14.399
and I'll get the ball rolling
by calling her a moron.

17:14.401 --> 17:15.566
My office.

17:15.568 --> 17:16.868
And it is thrilling

17:16.870 --> 17:19.103
to finally be on
the same page for once.

17:19.105 --> 17:21.039
I'm so sorry
about all of this, Earl.

17:21.041 --> 17:22.807
I never should've
shown her that movie.

17:22.809 --> 17:25.376
It's just too dirty
for a child to handle.

17:25.378 --> 17:27.111
I get it.
I'm a parent, too.

17:27.113 --> 17:29.747
Our job is to save these kids
from themselves,

17:29.749 --> 17:33.017
even if it means crushing
a dream or two.

17:33.019 --> 17:33.651
Good luck.

17:33.653 --> 17:36.687
<i> It turned out, my mom</i>
<i> was living "dirty dancing,"</i>

17:36.689 --> 17:37.422
<i> but she wasn't Baby --</i>

17:37.424 --> 17:40.291
<i> she was her</i>
<i> controlling parent,</i>
<i> Jerry Orbach,</i>

17:40.293 --> 17:44.028
<i> and that was a role</i>
<i> she refused to play.</i>

17:44.030 --> 17:46.431
Mom,
I know I screwed up...

17:46.433 --> 17:47.698
Humiliated myself.

17:47.700 --> 17:51.202
Got cake in my ear
and inhaled some confetti.

17:51.204 --> 17:54.338
And I'm grounded for life,
which I deserve.

17:54.340 --> 17:56.841
No, you don't.

17:56.943 --> 17:58.276
What?

17:58.278 --> 18:02.313
So, you wanted to live
"dirty dancing."

18:02.315 --> 18:05.216
Nobody gets that
more than me.

18:05.218 --> 18:07.885
I'd love to be Baby
(chuckles)

18:07.887 --> 18:09.720
Get swept off my feet

18:09.722 --> 18:13.291
and spun around
the dance floor.

18:14.194 --> 18:17.528
Honestly,
it's all I've ever wanted.

18:17.530 --> 18:18.930
[ Chuckles ]

18:19.399 --> 18:21.933
I know it can't happen
for me,

18:21.935 --> 18:26.704
but, uh,
it still can for you.

18:26.973 --> 18:28.106
What are you saying?

18:28.108 --> 18:31.576
Nobody puts my baby
in a corner.

18:31.578 --> 18:33.211
<i> And so, with the help</i>
<i> of our mom,</i>

18:33.213 --> 18:36.414
<i> Erica cleaned herself off</i>
<i> and took center stage</i>

18:36.416 --> 18:39.650
<i> to have the time of her life.</i>

