19:10.517 --> 19:12.817
What in heaven's name
is happening?

19:12.819 --> 19:15.987
I brought you here to shut
this nonsense down,

19:15.989 --> 19:16.821
not make it worse!

19:16.823 --> 19:18.856
The dirty dance
is back on!

19:18.858 --> 19:22.827
You might want to Orbach
these kids, but not me.

19:22.829 --> 19:24.929
I Miss the '50s.
