<i> Sure, we didn't magically do</i>
<i> the same dance number</i>

19:53.226 --> 19:53.991
<i> like in the movies.</i>

19:53.993 --> 19:56.427
<i> In fact, most of us weren't</i>
<i> good dancers at all.</i>

19:56.429 --> 20:00.665
<i> But for the first time,</i>
<i> it didn't seem to matter.</i>

