<i> my mom wasn't just watching</i>
<i> "dirty dancing"</i>

20:34.934 --> 20:36.033
<i> For the 18th time.</i>

20:36.035 --> 20:38.836
<i> She was living it</i>
<i> for the very first.</i>

20:38.838 --> 20:40.338
<i> It's all she ever wanted.</i>

20:40.340 --> 20:44.041
¶  <i> No, I Never Felt</i>
